					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Eve MacDonald</h4>
												<p>Eve MacDonald is an ancient historian, archaeologist, and senior lecturer in ancient history at Cardiff University. One of the world’s foremost experts on the history and material culture of Carthage, North Africa, and the Middle East, she is the author of <em>Hannibal</em>. When not teaching in Cardiff, she lives in London.</p>
